  "body": "In German you order the sentence differently\r\n\r\n        \"vor 1 Minute\"\r\nnot \r\n        \"1 minute ago\"\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/status-im/status-react/blob/develop/src/status_im/translations/de.cljs#L57\r\n\r\nSo the strategy for I18n should be to always inerpolate the prases, e.g. \"{{value}} minute ago\", \"vor {{value}} Minute\".\r\n\r\n\r\n",
